        <updateDate>2020-10-06T19:29:21Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Helping Health Care Workers Afford Child and Elder Care Act</b><br> <br> This bill provides funding for FY2020 for child and adult-dependent care services for essential workers. Essential workers include (1) health-sector employees, (2) emergency responders, (3) sanitation workers, (4) employees of businesses required to remain open during the public health emergency declared on January 31, 2020, and (5) other workers a state deems essential and who are unable to telework. Eligibility for such funding is not based on income.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
